      "note": "The rule of modesty applies to men as well as women. A brazen stare by a man at a woman (or even at a man) is a breach of refined manners. Where sex is concerned, modesty is not only \"good form\": it is not only to guard the weaker sex, but also to guard the spiritual good of the stronger sex."
